title: Albania Food Inflation
description: Cost of food in Albania increased 14.60 percent in September of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Food Inflation in Albania averaged 4.35 percent from 2008 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 14.90 percent in August of 2022 and a record low of -1.40 percent in February of 2012. This page provides - Albania Food Inflation - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Instituti i Statistikave (INSTAT)
